---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - RANDOBLOG" description="The pressure valve for thoughts that don't fit anywhere else.">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
        <div class="space-y-16">

            <!-- Hero / Mission -->
            <section>
                <div class="space-y-5 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tight">
                        What is RANDOBLOG?
                    </h1>
                    <p>
                        Most of what's in my head at any given time has no business staying there. Sensor architectures for detecting things that probably don't exist, monetary policy arguments with myself at 3 AM, half-finished propulsion math on the back of a grocery receipt. RANDOBLOG is where all of that goes so I can stop thinking about it and move on to the next thing I won't finish.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Nothing here is peer-reviewed. Some of it is probably wrong. The point was never to be authoritative. It's a pressure valve for the kind of thinking that doesn't fit neatly into a job description or a conversation at a party. If something here turns out to be useful to someone, that's a happy accident. If it doesn't, at least it's out of my head and I can sleep.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Divider -->
            <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent-primary/30 to-transparent"></div>

            <!-- About Me -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-8">About Me</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Credentials</div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">None that would impress a hiring committee, but I own a suspicious number of lab coats.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-secondary/40 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Experimental Skills</div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Adept at pushing buttons I probably shouldn't and Googling "is it supposed to smoke like that?"</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Focus</div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Whatever currently keeps me awake at 2 AM: quantum weirdness, black holes, or why my coffee tastes metallic.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-secondary/40 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Long-Term Goal</div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">To someday be mistaken for an actual scientist in a dimly lit conference hallway.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Divider -->
            <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent-secondary/30 to-transparent"></div>

            <!-- Projects -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-2">Projects</h2>
                <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 text-sm">Things I've built when I probably should have been sleeping.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

                    <a href="https://onon.me" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">onon.me</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-primary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">A private, local-first personal vault. Tag, save, and organize fragments of thought without handing your data to anyone. Everything stays on your device.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://btcar.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-secondary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-secondary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors">btcar.app</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-secondary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">Point your camera at any price tag and instantly see its Bitcoin value. Real-time OCR detection with AR overlay. All processing on-device, no data leaves your phone.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://job.rip" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">job.rip</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-primary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">A satirical "AI Labor Transition Authority" that performs career autopsies on your job title. Enter your profession, receive a darkly comedic report on how AI plans to replace you.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://apophis.bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-secondary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-secondary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors">apophis.bot</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-secondary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">An interactive 3D orbital simulator for asteroid 99942 Apophis. Visualize the 2029 close approach that threads the needle between Earth and our satellites.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://hodl.pub" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-primary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">hodl.pub</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-primary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">100 Bitcoin rules to live by. Self-custody, security, monetary philosophy, and the ideological foundations of decentralized money.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://sentio.bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-secondary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-secondary/5 transition-all duration-300">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-primary transition-colors">sentio.bot</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-secondary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">A 3D interactive simulation for modeling consciousness. Explore how information integration and self-referential processing produce consciousness scores across systems.</p>
                    </a>

                    <a href="https://globb.bot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group block p-5 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50 hover:border-accent-primary/40 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent-primary/5 transition-all duration-300 md:col-span-2">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                            <span class="text-accent-primary font-semibold group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors">globb.bot</span>
                            <span class="text-text-muted/40 text-xs group-hover:text-accent-primary/60 transition-colors">&#x2197;</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed">A canvas-based interactive visualization. Best experienced rather than explained.</p>
                    </a>

                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Divider -->
            <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-accent-primary/30 to-transparent"></div>

            <!-- Colophon -->
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-8">Colophon</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Math</div>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Full LaTeX rendering via KaTeX. Because if you can't put an equation in it, what's the point.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Source</div>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Every article links to its markdown on GitHub. Synced on push so bad ideas update in real time.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-secondary rounded-xl border border-border-color/50">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Scope</div>
                        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Physics, AI, Bitcoin, space, consciousness, and anything else that won't leave me alone at night.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <section class="text-center py-8">
                <a href="/" class="btn-primary text-lg px-8 py-4">
                    Read the posts
                </a>
            </section>

        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
